{"id":611391,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/05/611391/","date":"2019-05-29T17:50:03Z","modified":"2019-05-29T17:55:07Z","title":"新浪科技 | B站声明：因弹幕系统技术升级 将暂停关闭弹幕功能","content":"<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-611389\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/d807-hxsrwwq7568060.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"578\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/d807-hxsrwwq7568060.png 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/d807-hxsrwwq7568060-285x300.png 285w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>新浪科技讯 5月29日晚间消息，B站官方微博发布声明称，因弹幕系统技术升级，从即日起至6月6日网站将暂停关闭弹幕功能。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-611387\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/89b6-hxsrwwq7572517.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"610\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/89b6-hxsrwwq7572517.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/89b6-hxsrwwq7572517-221x300.jpg 221w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>今日稍早时间，部分网友反映，虎牙、斗鱼等直播平台出现弹幕断流现象，用户观看直播时无法同步观看横屏弹幕。</p>\n<p>据了解，昨日，YY直播发布系统升级维护通知公告；今日，虎牙发布系统维护通知。弹幕断流或与系统维护有关。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-611390\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/dfc3-hxsrwwq7359705.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"399\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/dfc3-hxsrwwq7359705.png 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/dfc3-hxsrwwq7359705-300x218.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-611388\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/af01-hxsrwwq7359575.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"294\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/af01-hxsrwwq7359575.png 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/af01-hxsrwwq7359575-300x160.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>目前，斗鱼也已发布微博回应称，弹幕飘屏功能正在系统升级。</p>\n","author":1003,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19985,36080,25235]}